<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>List</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/menu/MenuList.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 100%;
        }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .sidebar {
            flex-basis: 20%;
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #333;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .mainpage {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 1rem;

        }
        .menu_title{
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .menu_sub{
            background-color: orange;
            width: 1000px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        #btn_menu{
            width: 100px;
            height: 30px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-left: 50px;

        }
        .image h2{
            text-align:left;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .image{
            /* border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            /* font-size: 30px; */
        }
        h5 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        ul li a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
        }
        #btn_submit{
            width: 490px;
            height: 40px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .finish_space{
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        .finish_space p{
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<form action="/menu/new" method="post">
  <main class="container">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <p>사장님 페이지</p>
        <h5> > 가게 정보</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="StoreAdd.mustache">가게 등록</a></li>
            <li><a href="StoreEdit.mustache">가게 수정</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">리뷰 관리</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 매출 관리</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">오늘의 매출</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">월 매출</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">년 매출</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 예약 관리</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">이번 주 예약</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">지난 예약</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 공지 사항</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">서비스 소개</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
        <section class="mainpage" style="overflow-y: scroll;">
            <fieldset >
                <div>
                    <br>
                    <p><img src="img/check.png" width="20px">   메뉴</p></div><br>
                <div class="menu_title">
                    전체메뉴 페이지 입니다.
                </div><br>
                <div class="menu_sub">
                    <button id="btn_menu">메뉴조회</button>
                    <button id="btn_menu">메뉴등록</button>
                    <button id="btn_menu">메뉴수정</button>
                </div><br>
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="col">번호</th>
                        <th scope="col">이름</th>
                        <th scope="col">가격</th>
                        <th scope="col">인기</th>
                        <th scope="col">설명</th>
                        <th scope="col">사진</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {{#menuList}}
                        <tr>
                            <td><a href="/menu/{{id}}">{{id}}</a></td>
                            <th>{{name}}</th>
                            <td>{{menu_price}}</td>
                            <th>{{popular}}</th>
                            <td>{{content}}</td>
                            <td>{{photo}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    {{/menuList}}
                    </tbody>
                </table><br><br>
                <div>
                    <div class="finish_space">
                        <p><button id="btn_submit"><a href="/menu/new">메뉴 추가</a></button></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
        </section>
      </main>
</form>
    </body>
</html>